THIRD-PARTY MEDIA AND SERVICES

The following third-party resources are used by ThunderPass:

BACKGROUND MUSIC
	Title:  "Mii Plaza Afternoon"
	Author: guilhermelimait
	Source: https://suno.com/song/56ede060-a891-421f-8f39-e420cd8adc2b
	Generated with Suno AI (https://suno.com)

AVATAR IMAGES — DiceBear
	ThunderPass uses the DiceBear "big-smile" avatar style to generate
	user avatars. Avatars are fetched at runtime from the DiceBear API.
	API:    https://api.dicebear.com/9.x/big-smile/svg
	Website: https://dicebear.com
	License: DiceBear avatars are released under CC0 1.0 Universal.

RETRO GAMING DATA — RetroAchievements
	ThunderPass optionally integrates with RetroAchievements to display
	user gaming stats and achievement data on player cards.
	We thank the RetroAchievements community for providing a free,
	open API for retro gaming data.
	API Docs: https://api-docs.retroachievements.org/
	Website:  https://retroachievements.org
	Images:   https://media.retroachievements.org
